and Kenya
Communication on false imprisonment, dated August 30, 1989
1. The African Commission on Human and Peoples' Rights, established under Article 30 of the African
Charter on Human and Peoples' Rights;
2. Meeting at its Sixth Ordinary Session held from 23rd October to 4th November 1989;
3. Considering that the communication is directed against States not parties to the African Charter on
Human and Peoples' Rights;

Declares the communication inadmissible (Article 101 of the Rules of Procedure).

